  "reasoning": "The article describes the synthesis and characterization of BiOX (X = Cl, Br, I) nanostructures and their enzyme-like activities. The BiOI nanonetworks exhibit superior peroxidase-like activity compared to BiOCl and BiOBr nanosheets. The activity can be further enhanced by depositing metals or metal oxides onto the BiOI nanonetworks. Specifically, Au NPs/BiOI nanocomposites show enhanced oxidase-like activity, while NiO NPs/BiOI nanocomposites show enhanced peroxidase-like activity. The article also details the kinetic parameters for the catalytic activities of these nanostructures and their application in sensing Hg2+ and Pb2+ ions."
